    "desc": "Jadida Mondrago, capital of the Republic of Cala Mondrago, is a sunny, Moorish island city-state in the Mediterranean, influenced by Steampunk and Dieselpunk, roughly from the year 188x. Tourists are welcome to visit. Roleplay participation is optional. The Mondragon islands are a longtime fixture of the Steamlands and are busy with residents from other steampunk-themed regions, wanderers, companions, and diplomats. It has a busy port with warehouses full of coffee, bolts of silk, bags of spices, more coffee, machinery and engineering tools from workshops across Africa and Arabia, and more coffee."
